              "text": "Lord Jesus, let nothing unholy remain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Apply Thine own blood and extract every stain;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To get this blest cleansing I all things forego;"
